sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant C as test_mcp_client
    participant L as LLM (ChatOpenAI)
    participant S as MCP Server

    U->>S: Start MCP HTTP Server (uvicorn on http://127.0.0.1:8000/sse)
    U->>C: Run test_mcp_client.py
    C->>S: Connect to MCP Server via sse_client
    S-->>C: SSE channel ready
    C->>S: List the tool available from the MCP Server
    S-->>C: Send the tool specs back

    U->>C: Enter user request
    C->>L: Send prompt containing tool specs + user request
    L-->>C: Return appropriate tool {"tool": "...", "arguments": {...}}

    C->>S: Call appropriate tool(tool, arguments)
    S-->>C: Tool result
    C-->>U: Print result
